      • SimulinkLine

        public SimulinkLine(SimulinkOutPort sourcePort,
                    SimulinkInPort destPort,
                    SimulinkBlock container)
        Creates a new line. This adds the line to the ports.
        Parameters:
        sourcePort - the source port (or null for unconnected source).
        destPort - the destination port (or null for unconnected destination).
        container - the containing block (never null).

      • obtainLayoutData

        @ADeepCloneTestExclude
public LineLayoutData obtainLayoutData()
        Returns the layout data for this line. This data is parsed from the model with each call, so repeated access should be avoided by storing the result in a local variable.

      • obtainLabelData

        @ADeepCloneTestExclude
public LabelLayoutData obtainLabelData()
        Returns the layout data for the label of this line or null if no label is available. This data is parsed from the model with each call, so repeated access should be avoided by storing the result in a local variable.
